<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/luke-pollard> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Luke Pollard was appointed Minister of State in the Ministry of Defence on 6 September 2025. He was previously Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State in the Ministry of Defence from 9 July 2024 to 6 September 2025. He was elected as the MP for Plymouth Sutton and Devonport in July 2024."@en .
